52. Telegram From the Department of State to Secretary of State Haig’s Delegation in New YorkSource: Department of State, Central
                            Foreign Policy File, Electronic Telegrams, D810460–0174. Secret;
                            Immediate; Stadis. Drafted by Hormats; cleared by Alvin Adams (S/S) and Richard Erdman (S/S–O); approved by Clark. Haig was attending the UN General Assembly meeting in New York.
